{"tid":756427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上半年24名警犯案被捕　18人涉刑事　行動處長：應潔身自愛","createTime":"2018-07-26T04:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T05:26:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7f532b2fd3ab0139927601cc1d81b003f4217f97","tid":756427,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"警務處今日（25日）公布，本港今年上半年罪案情況持續平穩，整體罪案有2.65萬宗。被問到近期多了涉及警務人員犯罪的報道，警務處行動處處長鄧炳強回應表示，今上半年共有24名警務人員被捕，當中18人涉刑事、5人涉非刑事如交通違例，1人被其他執法部門拘捕。鄧炳強表示，警方絕不會偏私，身為執法者更應「潔身自愛」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/215047/%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B424%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%A6%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-18%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B-%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7-%E6%87%89%E6%BD%94%E8%BA%AB%E8%87%AA%E6%84%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F215047%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B424%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-18%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%25BD%2594%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2584%259B&d=8FrzdiQ2b%2F56ccVZZcMyFGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=ce551b2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/215047/%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B424%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%A6%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-18%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B-%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7-%E6%87%89%E6%BD%94%E8%BA%AB%E8%87%AA%E6%84%9B</a>"},{"pid":"4cf3000a92691d77b31b568eb4a9910617e1ddd1","tid":756427,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"咪又係循例遣責下講下兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 官官相衛做個樣"},{"pid":"b6a041a71324ab4349848306f39407494a074a52","tid":756427,"uid":58552,"like":0,